{"arkId":"cl010104370","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104370","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1740 - 1760","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 6","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1740,"endYear":1760,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Truitte et Mourier","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6235","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde, sur le fond une sc\u00e8ne de taverne \u00e9maill\u00e9e, trois hommes buvant et fumant. Sc\u00e8ne entour\u00e9e de plusieurs motifs \u00e9maill\u00e9s : bouteille, carafe, instruments de musique, fleurs. Poussoir orn\u00e9 d\u0027un brillant, charni\u00e8re moulur\u00e9e, la lunette du verre d\u00e9cor\u00e9e de fleurs. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes, aiguilles serties de roses de diamant. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre avec potence ajustable, d\u0027une fus\u00e9e \u00e0 cha\u00eene et d\u0027un balancier \u00e0 ressort-spiral-r\u00e9glant. Coq circulaire d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de rinceaux reperc\u00e9s, rosette de r\u00e9glage en argent grav\u00e9e de